 wealthy have taken the highest degrees and blessed ranks!\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cHow is that?\u201d They said, \u201cThey pray as we pray, they fast as we fast, they give in\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7686,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/05\/prophet-never-says-no-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":28823,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: The Prophet never refused to give in charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 5, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, was never asked anything for which he said no. Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5687, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2311 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064f\u0626\u0650\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0634\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0621\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0637\u064f\u0651 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0644\u064e\u0627\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"sel